json{
  "title": "Cold Genesis Cosmology: Analytical Solver and Emergent Metric Validation Package",
  "description": "This repository provides the reproducible core computational framework for Cold Genesis Cosmology (CGC). It implements the symbolic metric tensor derivations for the emergent Painlevé-Gullstrand acoustic metric, validates Parameterized Post-Newtonian (PPN) gamma compliance, and numerically solves the phase-shifted acoustic horizon projections for cosmic microwave background (CMB) multipole peaks.",
